title: You’re Never Too Busy To Lose Weight
itunes:title: You’re Never Too Busy To Lose Weight
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

Today's live is for the people who are trapped in the "I'm too busy" cycle to lose weight.

We all do it. We blame our kids, jobs, and lives for sucking up all of our time.

This approach is unique. You are going to learn how to change how you think. You don't need MORE time. You don't need to change your life. You need to take ownership of your choices on how you spend your time.
